name: Drawingroom Sessions #1
description:
This started as a pen and ink sketch in the Artdamaged Studios "drawingroom", which is a physical space intended for collaboration and socializing with my artist friends. After only a few session, pandemic quarantine started and it's been just me and the cats. Stella is hanging with me in this meta/self-portrait, as the drawingroom has become subject rather than a gathering spot; however, I'm pleased to share it with you and I hope that it will continue to be be a catalyst for creativity and inspiration. I have more drawings and some music created in the drawingroom that I'm excited to share with you. 

As they say, "The first one's free." ;)

~Joel
